{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"LDC4","author":"Weedust"}},"tagMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>相关链接：\n<a href=\"https://www.webpackjs.com/guides/\">官方文档（中文）</a>\n<a href=\"http://webpack.wuhaolin.cn/\">深入浅出Webpack</a></p>\n<p>每搭建一个项目，都会用到的东西就是构建工具，每次搭建完，就基本上不会去修改了。<br>\n但每次手动搭建，似乎都会存在各种奇葩的问题，因为构建工具的版本迭代还是非常快的。<br>\n尽管webpack的文档是如此详细，但还是会踩到一些坑。<br>\n在这种间歇性一次性使用情况下，配置项经常搞忘。  </p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/webpack/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-09 09:21:42","title":"重拾Webpack","tags":["webpack","工程化"],"category":"学习","draft":null}}}]},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>相关链接：\n<a href=\"https://juejin.im/post/5b9346dcf265da0aac6fbe57\">前端优化：浏览器缓存技术介绍</a></p>\n<p>前些天，被人问到浏览器缓存，突然感觉我对浏览器好陌生。\n平时，开发只会勾上</p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/browser-cache/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-23 19:45:36","title":"浏览器缓存","tags":["缓存","浏览器"],"category":"学习","draft":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>相关链接：\n<a href=\"https://www.webpackjs.com/guides/\">官方文档（中文）</a>\n<a href=\"http://webpack.wuhaolin.cn/\">深入浅出Webpack</a></p>\n<p>每搭建一个项目，都会用到的东西就是构建工具，每次搭建完，就基本上不会去修改了。<br>\n但每次手动搭建，似乎都会存在各种奇葩的问题，因为构建工具的版本迭代还是非常快的。<br>\n尽管webpack的文档是如此详细，但还是会踩到一些坑。<br>\n在这种间歇性一次性使用情况下，配置项经常搞忘。  </p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/webpack/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-09 09:21:42","title":"重拾Webpack","tags":["webpack","工程化"],"category":"学习","draft":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>相关链接：\n<a href=\"https://eggjs.org/zh-cn/intro/quickstart.html\">官方文档（中文）</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/eggjs/egg/\">Github</a></p>\n<p>最近依赖别人的背景图片接口挂掉了，索性自己搭建一个nodejs服务来提供每日必应图。<br>\n之前有看过koa2，做微信小程序有用过wafer2的server端。<br>\n比较知名的还是eggjs，基于koa封装的企业级nodejs框架。  </p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/eggjs/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-06-25 19:03:17","title":"eggjs学习与实践","tags":["nodejs","框架"],"category":"学习","draft":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>相关链接：\n<a href=\"https://zh-hans.reactjs.org/docs/hooks-intro.html\">官方文档（中文）</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/dt-fe/weekly/blob/master/79.%E7%B2%BE%E8%AF%BB%E3%80%8AReact%20Hooks%E3%80%8B.md\">精读React Hooks</a>\n<a href=\"https://juejin.im/post/5ccd3f8fe51d455c6049b7e6?utm_source=gold_browser_extension\">拥抱React Hooks</a></p>\n<p>为什么要创造Hook？</p>\n<ol>\n<li>在组件之间复用状态逻辑很难 （这个可以理解）</li>\n<li>复杂组件变得难以理解（任何组件复杂了，都会变得难以理解）</li>\n<li>难以理解的class（class还是很好用的）</li>\n</ol>\n","fields":{"slug":"/react-hooks/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-05-07 12:25:53","title":"React Hooks","tags":["react","新特性"],"category":"学习","draft":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>如果面试你的人，不是搞前端的，或者是组长、总监、GM以上的<br>\n基本上都会问基础知识，例如：https、浏览器从输入url之后都经历了什么</p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/interview/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-01-23 14:17:21","title":"面试基础知识汇总","tags":null,"category":"面试","draft":true}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>从大学本科毕业后，出来工作已经一年半了。<br>\n经历了很多，但成长感觉还是很慢。要是再这样下去，就没救了。<br>\n最好，还是拟定一个计划，然后一步步实现下去。</p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/2019-plan/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-01-06 19:17:58","title":"2019年工作学习计划","tags":null,"category":"计划","draft":true}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"<p>采用<a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby\">gatsby</a>来搭建博客<br>\nGatsby v2: Blazing fast modern site generator for React</p>\n","fields":{"slug":"/hello-gatsby-blog/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-01-06 17:44:58","title":"README","tags":["hello-world"],"category":"readme","draft":true}}}]},"allNavigationJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"name":"分类","link":"/cats"}},{"node":{"name":"标签","link":"/tags"}}]}},"pageContext":{"tag":"webpack"}}